text: Victoria Muntean (born 23 January 1997) is a French professional tennis player. Muntean has a career-high WTA singles ranking of 435, attained on 27 June 2016, and a career-high WTA doubles ranking of 408, reached on 24 July 2017. She has won three singles and six doubles titles on tournaments of the ITF Circuit. ==Career== Muntean made her WTA Tour doubles main-draw debut at the 2011 Internationaux de Strasbourg, partnering Dia Evtimova; they lost in the first round to the fourth-seeded pair of Akgul Amanmuradova and Chuang Chia-jung. ==ITF Circuit finals== {|class=wikitable style="font-size:85%" !Legend |-
